Very sad to hear of the passing of Ray Skelly, who served as an NDP MP for 14 years. He was a dedicated advocate for his community, and was known as someone who went above and beyond to connect with people. Ray's family, friends, and community are in our thoughts.

Nous sommes tristes d'apprendre le décès de Ray Skelly, qui a été député du NPD pendant 14 ans. Il était un grand défenseur de sa communauté, reconnu pour se surpasser pour se rapprocher des gens. Les proches et la communauté de Ray sont dans nos pensées.
